## 5.1 Introduction to Collections

A collection is a data structure that holds multiple elements. Java provides the Collections Framework with various implementations.

### `ArrayList`

An ordered list that can grow dynamically.

```java
import java.util.ArrayList;

ArrayList<String> names = new ArrayList<>();
names.add("Alice");
