    PickResult pickResult = event.getPickResult();
    if (pickResult != null) {
        Node pickedNode = pickResult.getIntersectedNode();
        if (pickedNode instanceof Box) {
            Box square = (Box) pickedNode;
            // Highlight or interact with square
        }
    }
});
```

